Launched in Soweto and Thembisa, the billboard provided a platform to empower women with confidence to go into the workplace and a stage to let them shine. &#x201c;Working closely with Liquorice, we wanted to push the digital innovation boundaries and do something never done before in the FMCG space,&#x201d; said Surf brand manager, Sinovuyo Rodolo. It was this drive for innovation that paved the way for Liquorice to launch this "world-first" for an FMCG brand, added Miles Murphy, founder and CEO of the digital marketing agency.